sequenceDiagram
    participant QM as queryModel()<br/>生产者

    participant QMS as queryModelWithStreaming()<br/>流式+VCR包装
    participant A as ask()<br/>便利封装
    participant H as execAgentHook()<br/>hooks隔离执行

    QM->>QMS: yield* 透传所有事件
    Note over QMS: withStreamingVCR 透明包装
    QMS-->>QMS: 实时处理每个事件

    QM->>A: yield SDKMessage
    Note over A: for await 逐条转发
    A-->>A: yield 给 SDK 调用方

    QM->>H: yield message
    Note over H: for await 独立消费
    H-->>H: hook 逻辑完全隔离
